@node Zone10 "Keyboard shortcut"
Decrease pattern
----------------
Press @{b}Alt + CursorLeft@{ub} to go back 1 pattern.
@endnode

@node Zone11 "Keyboard shortcut"
Increase pattern
----------------
Press @{b}Alt + CursorRight@{ub} to go forward 1 pattern.
@endnode

@node Zone12 "Keyboard shortcut"
No keyboard shortcut available for this action.
@endnode

@node Zone13 "Keyboard shortcut"
No keyboard shortcut available for this action.
@endnode

@node Zone14 "Keyboard shortcut"
Goto Arrange Window
-------------------
Press @{b}Right Amiga + E@{ub} to goto the arrange window.
@endnode

@node Zone15 "Keyboard shortcut"
No keyboard shortcut available for this action.
@endnode

@node Zone16 "Keyboard shortcut"
Goto Workbench
--------------
Press @{b}Left Amiga + M@{ub} to go to the Workbench. Press it again, to go
back to 303tracker.
@endnode

@node Zone17 "Keyboard shortcut"
Play/Render Button
------------------
Press @{b}Shift + Right Amiga@{ub} to play the current pattern.

Press @{b}Shift + Alt@{ub} to play the whole song (made with the Arrange
Window) from the current position.

Press @{b}Right Amiga + R@{ub} to go to the Render menu.
@endnode

@node Zone31 "Keyboard shortcut"
Glide Column
------------
Press @{b}+@{ub} to switch glide at current mouseposition ON.
Press @{b}-@{ub} to switch glide at current mouseposition OFF.
@endnode

@node Zone32 "Keyboard shortcut"
Note Length Column
------------------
Press @{b}+@{ub} or @{b}-@{ub} to change note length at the current
mouseposition.
@endnode

@node Zone33 "Keyboard shortcut"
Pattern-Length
--------------
Press @{b}Alt + L@{ub} to get a requester where you can alter the length of
the pattern.
@endnode

