@node Index1 "Index"
Table of keyboard shortcuts in 303tracker:
------------------------------------------

@{b}Return@{ub}          - Play current note and move cursor 1 down
@{b}Space@{ub}           - Toggle edit on/off
@{b}Tab@{ub}             - Select next column to edit
@{b}Tab@{ub} + @{b}Shift@{ub}     - Select previous column to edit
@{b}Del@{ub}             - Kill current note and move cursor 1 down (If edit on)
@{b}Help@{ub}            - Online help (AmigaGuide)
@{b}Escape@{ub}          - Abort process (Cancel) or exit window
                         - Toggle edit on/off
@{b}Return@{ub}          - Confirm action (OK) and close window
                         - Preview current note
@{b}.@{ub}               - Toggle Edit-style (Draw, Line, or Zoomed)
@{b}Control@{ub}         - Locate mouse at selected position(column,note-position)

@{b}Cursor Up@{ub}       - Move cursor 1 up in note-column
@{b}Cursor Down@{ub}     - Move cursor 1 down in note-column
@{b}CursUp@{ub}+@{b}Shift@{ub}    - Move cursor 4 up in note-column
@{b}CursDn@{ub}+@{b}Shift@{ub}    - Move cursor 4 down in note-column
@{b}CursUp@{ub}+@{b}Ctrl@{ub}     - Move cursor 8 up in note-column AND holds at end
@{b}CursDn@{ub}+@{b}Ctrl@{ub}     - Move cursor 8 down in note-column AND holds at end


@{b}Cursor Left@{ub}     - Increase/transpose value with 10  (or 1 in Note Column)
@{b}Cursor Right@{ub}    - Decrease/transpose value with 10  (or 1 in Note Column)
@{b}CursLe@{ub}+@{b}Shift@{ub}    - Increase/transpose value with 100 (or 12 in Note Column)
@{b}CursRi@{ub}+@{b}Shift@{ub}    - Decrease/transpose value with 100 (or 12 in Note Column)

Same as:

@{b}+@{ub}               - Increase/transpose value with 10  (or 1 in Note Column)
@{b}-@{ub}               - Decrease/transpose value with 10  (or 1 in Note Column)
@{b}+@{ub} + @{b}Shift@{ub}       - Increase/transpose value with 100 (or 12 in Note Column)
@{b}-@{ub} + @{b}Shift@{ub}       - Decrease/transpose value with 100 (or 12 in Note Column)


@{b}F6@{ub}              - Set cursor at '00' in note-column
@{b}F7@{ub}              - Set cursor at '08' in note-column
@{b}F8@{ub}              - Set cursor at '16' in note-column
@{b}F9@{ub}              - Set cursor at '24' in note-column
@{b}F10@{ub}             - Set cursor at '31' in note-column

